Description: Up for sale is a 2017 Fender American Professional Stratocaster HSS Shawbucker Body with a custom Musikraft Maple Neck and Hardshell Case included. The color is Antique Olive. The body and electronics are all stock; the only change made was that I swapped the bent vintage steel saddles for stainless steel block saddles. I much prefer the block-style saddles (I think they're much more comfortable on the right hand and make palm muting much easier) but the original bent steel saddles are also included in case you prefer to put them back on instead (the Fender stamped neckplate is also included in this auction). Although I tried, I never really liked the stock neck very much, so it was replaced with a custom Musikraft neck (full specs listed below) and locking Fender tuners. The neck has a compound radius (like the American Deluxe Series Strats) and an oil-based finish (not sticky at all, feels very close to bare wood). The neck also had a genuine bone nut installed. The body and neck are both in excellent (like new) condition and have hardly been played. Gotta sell off a few guitars in order to buy a nice acoustic for a band I recently joined, so unfortunately as much as I'd love to have at least one strat in the arsenal this one's gotta go. The guitar has received a full professional fret level and setup, and is ready to ship out quickly! Thanks for looking!
